Start project
instalar dependencia do mongo ->  
	composer require jenssegers/mongodb  
	composer require mongodb/mongodb
change .env
alterar o database -> config/database.php (adicionar as config do mongodb)
adicinar ao provider mongodbserviceprovider -> config/database.php  Jenssegers\Mongodb\MongodbServiceProvider::class,

create o crud
Adicionar na model  connection  e collection e importar o tipo da model

https://github.com/jenssegers/laravel-mongodb 

